[315.249327, "o", "\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KB\bB\r\u001b[K           If omitted, default is tabular for most commands. For the commands\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[7m Manual page nmcli(1) line 78 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KB\bB\r\u001b[K           producing more structured information, that cannot be displayed on a\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[7m Manual page nmcli(1) line 79 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
