[315.279799, "o", "           single line, default is multiline. Currently, they are:\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[7m Manual page nmcli(1) line 80 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KB\bB\r\u001b[K\u001b[m"]
