[335.769826, "o", "       \u001b[1m-t \u001b[22m| \u001b[1m--terse\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[7m Manual page nmcli(1) line 95 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KB\bB\r\u001b[K           Output is terse. This mode is designed and suitable for computer (script)\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[7m Manual page nmcli(1) line 96 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KB\bB\r\u001b[K           processing.\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[7m Manual page nmcli(1) line 97 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
