[354.8645, "o", "\r\n\u001b[24;1H\r\u001b[K\u001b[7m Manual page nmcli(1) line 209 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KA\bA\r\u001b[K"]
